00:56:08.190 --> 00:56:11.910
So for me, any
type of meditation,

00:56:11.910 --> 00:56:14.280
the goal of that
meditation comes

00:56:14.280 --> 00:56:17.100
down to what is your
goal about the person

00:56:17.100 --> 00:56:18.480
that you want to
be in the world.

00:56:18.480 --> 00:56:21.240
And actually, it's not
so much like how can I

00:56:21.240 --> 00:56:26.910
be a good meditator and
just embody whatever

00:56:26.910 --> 00:56:30.000
