24 brand new hours to be alive.

01:07:06.130 --> 01:07:09.820
I vow to look at living beings
with the eyes of compassion.

01:07:09.820 --> 01:07:11.020
So you say that.

01:07:11.020 --> 01:07:14.860
So there is
moment-to-moment practice.

